 CREATE A TABLE


<table>
used to create the table itself.

<thead>, <tbody>
not manadatory but org is recommeneded.

<tr>

define the  a table  row.

<th> define a table header cell
<td> define a table data cell
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title > table </title

</head>
<body> 

<table border="2">
<tr> 

<th>days</th>
<th>period1</th>

<th>period2</th>

<th> period3</th>

</tr>
<tr>

<td>monday</td>

<td>maths</td>
<td>sceine</td>
<td>games</td>

</tr>
<tr>

<td>tuesday</td>

<td>phys</td>
<td>sceine</td>
<td>games</td>

</tr>
<tr>

<td>thursadyu</td>

<td> gap</td>
